To download a video:
yt-dlp "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4ofJpOEXrZs"

To list available formats for a video:
yt-dlp --list-formats "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4ofJpOEXrZs"

To download the best 720p MP4 video, best audio, and combined into an MP4:
yt-dlp -f "bestvideo[height<=?720][ext=mp4]+bestaudio/best[ext=mp4]/best" --recode mp4 "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4ofJpOEXrZs"

